<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">ENG101 - Syllabus</span></strong></p>
<p>Objectives</p>
<ul><li>The student will learn to effectively use the fundamentals of the English language through discussion, short essays,  and a final term paper.</li></ul>
<p>Lessons</p>
<ul><li>16 lessons (2x a week)</li></ul>
<p>Scoring</p>
<ul><li>Participation (20% total grade)</li><li>5 short essays (40% total grade)</li><li>1 term paper (40% total grade)</li></ul>
<p></p>
